        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Terms and conditions of the Offer : "
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                79,
                78,
                392,
                92
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "list",
            "content": {
                "list_type": "text_list",
                "list_items": [
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "1. Offer is only applicable to successful applications for Target Saving Pro policies (single premium) submitted via Electronic Sales System (ePOS) between 1 January 2026 and 28 February 2026 (both dates inclusive) and issued by Well Link Life Insurance Company Limited (‘Well Link Life’) on or before 31 March 2026 (the ‘Eligible Policy(ies)’). Policy is not eligible for this Offer if the application is not submitted via Electronic Sales System (ePOS). "
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "2. Subject to the fulfillment of the terms and conditions hereof, the Offer is considered as part of the policy. "
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "3. The premium discount amount will be used in offsetting the premium of the Eligible Polic(ies) when it falls due. The policyowner only needs to pay the net premium, which will be equal to the single premium or first year annual premium minus the corresponding premium discount amount. Premium levy will be calculated based on the net premium under the Offer. If the premium of the Eligible Policy is increased or decreased during cooling-off period, the premium discount amount will be calculated based on the latest adjusted premium. The premium discount amount will be rounded to the nearest two decimal places in the policy currency. The premium discount cannot be transferred or redeemed for cash. "
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "4. Well Link Life reserves the right to suspend or cancel the Offer, amend the terms and conditions at any time without prior notice. "
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
